    <item>
      <title>奥尔班再次威胁否决俄罗斯对天然气运输的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/orban-renews-threat-to-veto-russia-sanctions-over-gas-transit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班再次威胁说，如果乌克兰未能在六个月内恢复俄罗斯天然气输送，他将在欧盟对俄罗斯的制裁到期时否决制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/orban-renews-threat-to-veto-russia-sanctions-over-gas-transit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 07:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Orsted 首席执行官因未能扭转风电行业颓势而辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/orsted-ceo-steps-down-after-failing-to-turn-around-wind-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在过去几年中，丹麦风电开发商 Orsted A/S 在大西洋两岸进行了一系列巨额减记后，Mads Nipper 将辞去该公司首席执行官一职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/orsted-ceo-steps-down-after-failing-to-turn-around-wind-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 07:16:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nationwide 称，2025 年初英国房价将停滞不前</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/uk-house-prices-disappoint-with-0-1-gain-nationwide-data-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据英国全国建筑协会的数据，今年年初英国房价几乎没有上涨，这表明房地产市场可能最终屈服于高昂的借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/uk-house-prices-disappoint-with-0-1-gain-nationwide-data-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 07:08:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾基准股指较 10 月高点下跌 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/philippine-benchmark-index-declines-20-from-october-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心潜在的全球逆风和令人失望的国内经济数据，菲律宾股市连续第五天下跌，导致该国基准指数进入熊市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/philippine-benchmark-index-declines-20-from-october-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 05:37:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
