    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行可能最早在 3 月份取消“限制性”政策标签</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/ecb-may-drop-restrictive-label-on-rate-stance-as-soon-as-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据了解欧洲央行理事会辩论情况的人士透露，欧洲央行可能在 3 月份的下一次决定中不再将其货币政策立场描述为“限制性的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/ecb-may-drop-restrictive-label-on-rate-stance-as-soon-as-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 17:19:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
